%sql 
select count(event) pv
From pv 
where type='track' and event='pageview'

%sql 
select count(tkid) uv
from(
    select distinct tkid,event
    From pv 
    where type='track' and event='pageview'
) a

df.registerTempTable("pv")%sql
select count(event) es,event
from pv
where type='track'
group by event
order by es desc
limit 1

%sql
select b.*,a.pvs from pv b right join(
    select count(event) pvs,tkid
    from pv
    where type='track' and event='pageview'
    group by tkid
    
) a
where b.tkid=a.tkid
order by pvs desc
limit 1
